Titolo: Everybody's Golf Portable 2

Anno: 2007

Descrizione: Everybody's Golf Portable 2 (みんなのGOLF ポータブル2, Minna no Gorufu Pōtaburu Tsū), known as Everybody's Golf 2 in the PAL region (Australian version titled Everybody's Golf: Open Tee 2) and Hot Shots Golf: Open Tee 2 in North America, is the eighth game in the Everybody's Golf series and the second to be released for PlayStation Portable. The game featured an online mode where up to 16 players were able to play on a single course. The servers shut down on 5 December 2011, making it impossible to play online since then.

